title: High Elo Team.
body:
Hey guys, I want to put together a high elo team to compete in tournaments, scrims and just climb the ladder. I won't be playing but I'll put the side together. Any high plat/diamond or above and feel like playing in a team.

Add me ingame on Swaglizard

replies.body:
Me, thanks.

Peaked at D5 but Dynamic Queue is too hard to solo.
